asset.title: ProZ LED Light Bar Torture Test
asset.description:
We took our ProZ LED Light Bars to the deserts of California and put them to the ultimate test. From dragging it through sand and dust to beating it with a sledge hammer - our lights proved their toughness and quality over and over again. Check out this video to see if we finally found their match...
